OL,3,CWessex Water ordered to pay #11
OL,4,Cmillion over wastewater failures
OL,6,FWessex Water has been ordered to pay
OL,7,F#11 million by regulator Ofwat for
OL,8,Ffailures managing flows of sewage and
OL,9,Fwastewater.
OL,11,FThe company, which covers areas
OL,12,Fincluding Dorset, Somerset, Bristol
OL,13,Falong with parts of Wiltshire,
OL,14,FGloucestershire and Hampshire - will
OL,15,Falso have to take a number of steps
OL,16,Fincluding sealing sewer pipes and
OL,17,Finstalling extra monitoring equipment.
