OL,3,CWessex Water ordered to pay #11
OL,4,Cmillion over wastewater failures
OL,6,FIn response to the announcement,
OL,7,FWessex Water admitted it has "much
OL,8,Fmore to do" to tackle the problems
OL,9,Fwith wastewater, but stressed they had
OL,10,Fproposals in place to tackle the
OL,11,Ffailings that had been identified.
OL,13,FOfwat has told the company it will not
OL,14,Fbe able to cover the cost of the
OL,15,Fenforcement action through its
OL,16,Fcustomers or increases to bills.
OL,18,FHowever, it comes after the company
OL,19,Fput up its water bills by an average
OL,20,Fof 20%, or #113, this year.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
