OL,3,CWessex Water ordered to pay #11
OL,4,Cmillion over wastewater failures
OL,6,FLynn Parker, the Senior Director for
OL,7,FEnforcement at Ofwat said Wessex Water
OL,8,Fhad "failed to effectively operate,
OL,9,Fmaintain and upgrade its wastewater
OL,10,Fassets, which meant there were spills
OL,11,Ffrom storm overflows when there
OL,12,Fshouldn't have been".
OL,14,FShe added, "To their credit, (Wessex
OL,15,FWater) has been one of the more
OL,16,Fproactive in investigating and
OL,17,Frectifying the problems identified.
OL,18,FHowever, there remain breaches which
OL,19,Fmust be accounted for and corrected.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
