OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F438A1762974133
OL,3,CWessex Water ordered to pay #11
OL,4,Cmillion over wastewater failures
OL,6,F"We understand that the public wants
OL,7,Fto see transformative change. That is
OL,8,Fwhy we are prioritising this sector-
OL,9,Fwide investigation which has so far
OL,10,Fheld five wastewater companies to
OL,11,Faccount to the tune of #240m in
OL,12,Fenforcement redress, benefitting the
OL,13,Flocal environment and the customers
OL,14,Fthose companies serve."
OL,16,FWessex Water is now the sixth water
OL,17,Fcompany to face a penalty this year.
OL,18,FLast month, South West Water was
OL,19,Fordered to pay #24 million pounds
OL,20,Fafter an Ofwat investigation found
OL,21,Fsewage failures.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
