OL,3,CWessex Water ordered to pay #11
OL,4,Cmillion over wastewater failures
OL,6,FOfwat said Wessex Water has invested
OL,7,Fmore than #150 million since 2020 on
OL,8,Fupgrading storm overflows in its
OL,9,Fregion.
OL,11,FAccording to the regulator, Wessex
OL,12,FWater already has plans in place for
OL,13,F2025-30 to address many of the
OL,14,Fcompliance issues identified at its
OL,15,Fwastewater treatment works and network
OL,16,F- but there still remains further
OL,17,Fmeasures the company needs to take to
OL,18,Fensure it is fully compliant.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
