OL,3,CWessex Water ordered to pay #11
OL,4,Cmillion over wastewater failures
OL,6,FThe water company, which is owned by
OL,7,FMalaysian firm YTL, is required to
OL,8,Fhelp local landowners seal sewer pipes
OL,9,Fto prevent unnecessary groundwater
OL,10,Freaching Wessex Water's network as
OL,11,Fpart of the enforcement plans.
OL,13,FOfwat has also said it must reduce
OL,14,Fspills at specific storm overflows
OL,15,Fthrough investment, and install
OL,16,Fadditional monitoring equipment.
OL,18,FIn a statement Wessex Water referenced
OL,19,Fthe proposals it had in place to
OL,20,Ftackle the failings that had been
OL,21,Fidentified.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
