OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "We regret the
OL,7,Fimpact our wastewater performance has
OL,8,Fhad on customers and the environment.
OL,9,FWhen the issues at our treatment sites
OL,10,Fwere identified we were quick to fix
OL,11,Fthem, but we do agree that there is
OL,12,Fmuch more to do ` particularly in
OL,13,Fareas where groundwater enters the
OL,14,Fsewerage network and can result in
OL,15,Foverflows operating long after
OL,16,Frainfall events.
