OL,3,CWessex Water ordered to pay #11
OL,4,Cmillion over wastewater failures
OL,6,F"Looking ahead, we are planning a step
OL,7,Fchange in the maintenance of our
OL,8,Fsewerage infrastructure with
OL,9,Finvestment of #300 million in this
OL,10,Farea by 2030, with expansions to some
OL,11,Fof our key waste treatment sites
OL,12,Feither already underway or completed.
OL,14,F"We also continue to encourage
OL,15,Fsustainable rainwater management,
OL,16,Fensuring rain is returned to the
OL,17,Fenvironment near where it falls rather
OL,18,Fthan entering the sewer system."
